        "<kbd>2</kbd> <b>Hard</b> — you recalled it, but only with significant effort, hesitation, or after a long pause. The interval grows slightly.",
        "<kbd>3</kbd> <b>Good</b> — you recalled it correctly with normal effort. The standard grade; use this when recall was confident but not immediate.",
