      text: "A <b>leech</b> is a card you keep failing. A card is auto-flagged as a leech when its cumulative FSRS lapses reach 4 — that is, 4 reviews graded Again after leaving the new-card state. The threshold is fixed at 4; there is no per-card setting. You can also manually flag any card as a leech from the repair row.",
