      type: "p",
      text: "<strong>Retiring</strong> a card parks it out of active FSRS review while keeping its full history, lineage, and content intact. Use it for a low-value card that has matured well and no longer earns its review time — you have learned it thoroughly and do not want to keep being tested on it.",
